These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, juice
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, august
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, american
1. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the american##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage       | juice       | water |
| Birthday         | august | february  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Nationality   | american       | brazilian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, scooter
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, avocado
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Birthday      | february     | march |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Transport   | scooter  | bike      |
| Food         | grapefruit | avocado     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, blend
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, camping
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
2 different pets are kept: horse, mouse
1. the fan of country is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Cigar      | bluemaster | blend  |
| Hobby          | board-games    | camping   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Pet     | mouse     | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, mauve
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, daisy
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, ship
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the person who likes mauve is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Color      | lavender       | mauve |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Flower           | daisy | rose    |
| Transport   | boat           | ship   |

