.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing
City: nizza, colone
2 different games are played: backgammon, canasta
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | sudoku     |
| City   | nizza          | colone |
| Game           | backgammon          | canasta    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 